   410	##### Disable console output
   411	The console output can be disabled with 2 different options:
   412	1. With the `LogCaptor.disableConsoleOutput()` method
   413	2. With a logback-test.xml file, see below for the details.
   414	
   415	Add `logback-test.xml` to your test resources with the following content:
   416	```xml
   417	<configuration>
   418	   <statusListener class="ch.qos.logback.core.status.NopStatusListener" />
   419	</configuration>
   420	```
